 <span data-ttu-id="17edf-350">次C#の例では、<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> プロパティを `true`に設定する方法を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="17edf-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
